title: FOX Motocross Valley Fair Shop Signing
description:
Check out Ryan Dungey, Ken Roczen, and Ricky Carmichael before the Oakland
race stoking out fans at Fox's Valley Fair store! Jeff Emig was there to
Host too before he hit the airwaves for the SX TV broadcast on Saturday!
